      "bgName": "bg_story_task"
    },
    {
      "say": "A great performance is only made possible by the hours of practice that go into it... so first, we'll need to plan out the lessons.",
      "actor": 401230,
      "side": 2,
      "dir": 1,
      "nameColor": "#a9f548",
      "typewriter": {
        "speed": 0.05,
        "speedUp": 0.01
      },
      "painting": {
        "alpha": 0.3,
        "time": 1
      },
      "bgName": "bg_story_task"
    },
    {
      "actor": 201010,
      "side": 2,
      "dir": 1,
      "nameColor": "#a9f548",
      "say": "Today, we're joined by Ritsuko and Iori, idol advising specialists. It's great to have the two of you here!",
      "typewriter": {
        "speed": 0.05,
        "speedUp": 0.01
      },
      "action": [
        {
          "y": 45,
          "type": "shake",
          "dur": 0.15,
          "number": 2,
          "delay": 0,
          "x": 0
        }
      ],
      "painting": {
        "alpha": 0.3,
        "time": 1
      },
      "bgName": "bg_story_task"
    },
    {
      "actor": 10700030,
      "side": 2,
      "dir": 1,
      "nameColor": "#a9f548",
      "hidePaintEquip": true,
      "say": "Feel free to ask me anything. As a top-tier idol, there's no question I won't be able to answer! Hehe~",
      "typewriter": {
        "speed": 0.05,
        "speedUp": 0.01
      },
      "painting": {
        "alpha": 0.3,
        "time": 1
      },
      "bgName": "bg_story_task"
    },
    {
      "actor": 10700050,
      "side": 2,
      "dir": 1,
      "nameColor": "#a9f548",
      "hidePaintEquip": true,
      "say": "I'm a fairly experienced idol as well, so I'll be glad to help however I can!",
      "typewriter": {
        "speed": 0.05,
        "speedUp": 0.01
      },
      "painting": {
        "alpha": 0.3,
        "time": 1
      },
      "bgName": "bg_story_task"
    },
    {
      "say": "Great, let's dive right in then. When drafting a lesson plan, we have to first think about the areas that need the most improvement.",
      "actor": 401230,
      "side": 2,
      "dir": 1,
      "nameColor": "#a9f548",
      "typewriter": {
        "speed": 0.05,
        "speedUp": 0.01
      },
      "painting": {
        "alpha": 0.3,
        "time": 1
      },
      "bgName": "bg_story_task"
    },
    {
      "say": "Just as a point of reference, what do the two of you think are the most important things that idols should get from the lessons?",
      "actor": 401230,
      "side": 2,
      "dir": 1,
      "nameColor": "#a9f548",
      "typewriter": {
        "speed": 0.05,
        "speedUp": 0.01
      },
      "painting": {
        "alpha": 0.3,
        "time": 1
      },
      "bgName": "bg_story_task"
    },
    {
      "actor": 10700030,
      "side": 2,
      "dir": 1,
      "nameColor": "#a9f548",
      "hidePaintEquip": true,
      "say": "Let's see... Well, you can't put on a show unless the singing and dancing are on lock.",
      "typewriter": {
        "speed": 0.05,
        "speedUp": 0.01
      },
      "action": [
        {
          "y": 45,
          "type": "shake",
          "dur": 0.15,
          "number": 2,
          "delay": 0,
          "x": 0
        }
      ],
      "painting": {
        "alpha": 0.3,
        "time": 1
      },
      "bgName": "bg_story_task"
    },
    {
      "actor": 10700050,
      "side": 2,
      "dir": 1,
      "nameColor": "#a9f548",
      "expression": 4,
      "hidePaintEquip": true,
      "say": "I think expressiveness is also important. It's a big part of singing and dancing, but also carries over to a variety of other aspects.",
      "typewriter": {
        "speed": 0.05,
        "speedUp": 0.01
      },
      "painting": {
        "alpha": 0.3,
        "time": 1
      },
      "bgName": "bg_story_task"
    },
    {
      "say": "That's true. Without all three of those things, you can't even be an idol.",
      "actor": 201010,
      "side": 2,
      "dir": 1,
      "nameColor": "#a9f548",
      "typewriter": {
        "speed": 0.05,
        "speedUp": 0.01
      },
      "painting": {
        "alpha": 0.3,
        "time": 1
      },
      "bgName": "bg_story_task"
    },
    {
      "say": "All right. Let's make a lesson plan that revolves around these three things: singing, dancing, and expressiveness.",
      "actor": 401230,
      "side": 2,
      "dir": 1,
      "nameColor": "#a9f548",
      "typewriter": {
        "speed": 0.05,
        "speedUp": 0.01
      },
      "painting": {
        "alpha": 0.3,
        "time": 1
      },
      "bgName": "bg_story_task"
    },
    {
      "say": "However... I do think it's important to say that right now, I feel like I'm trying to plan without a specific goal in mind.",
      "actor": 401230,
      "side": 2,
      "dir": 1,
      "nameColor": "#a9f548",
      "typewriter": {
        "speed": 0.05,
        "speedUp": 0.01
      },
      "painting": {
        "alpha": 0.3,
        "time": 1
      },
      "bgName": "bg_story_task"
    },
    {
      "say": "Of course the end goal is to be able to put on a higher-quality performance, but that's rather vague and doesn't tell us what we need to do to get there.",
      "actor": 401230,
      "side": 2,
      "dir": 1,
      "nameColor": "#a9f548",
      "typewriter": {
        "speed": 0.05,
        "speedUp": 0.01
      },
      "painting": {
        "alpha": 0.3,
        "time": 1
      },
      "bgName": "bg_story_task"
    },
    {
      "actor": 10700030,
      "side": 2,
      "dir": 1,
      "nameColor": "#a9f548",
      "hidePaintEquip": true,
      "say": "Yeah~ It's definitely hard to see that when you first are starting out.",
      "typewriter": {
        "speed": 0.05,
        "speedUp": 0.01
      },
      "painting": {
        "alpha": 0.3,
        "time": 1
      },
      "bgName": "bg_story_task"
    },
    {
      "say": "Some say that training without a purpose is no better than not training at all.",
      "actor": 201010,
      "side": 2,
      "dir": 1,
      "nameColor": "#a9f548",
      "typewriter": {
        "speed": 0.05,
        "speedUp": 0.01
      },
      "painting": {
        "alpha": 0.3,
        "time": 1
      },
      "bgName": "bg_story_task"
    },
    {
      "say": "But how should we go about setting those tangible goals?",
      "actor": 201010,
      "side": 2,
      "dir": 1,
      "nameColor": "#a9f548",
      "typewriter": {
        "speed": 0.05,
        "speedUp": 0.01
      },
      "painting": {
        "alpha": 0.3,
        "time": 1
      },
      "bgName": "bg_story_task"
    },
    {
      "actor": 10700050,
      "side": 2,
      "dir": 1,
      "nameColor": "#a9f548",
      "hidePaintEquip": true,
      "say": "Why not start with something short-term first?",
      "typewriter": {
        "speed": 0.05,
        "speedUp": 0.01
      },
      "painting": {
        "alpha": 0.3,
        "time": 1
      },
      "bgName": "bg_story_task"
    },
    {
      "say": "Short-term, huh...",
      "actor": 401230,
      "side": 2,
      "dir": 1,
      "nameColor": "#a9f548",
      "typewriter": {
        "speed": 0.05,
        "speedUp": 0.01
      },
      "painting": {
        "alpha": 0.3,
        "time": 1
      },
      "bgName": "bg_story_task"
    },
    {
      "actor": 10700050,
      "side": 2,
      "dir": 1,
      "nameColor": "#a9f548",
      "expression": 2,
      "hidePaintEquip": true,
      "say": "That's right. Break down the things you want to achieve into small, realistic chunks that build up towards the final goal.",
      "typewriter": {
        "speed": 0.05,
        "speedUp": 0.01
      },
      "action": [
        {
          "y": 45,
          "type": "shake",
          "dur": 0.15,
          "number": 2,
          "delay": 0,
          "x": 0
        }
      ],
      "painting": {
        "alpha": 0.3,
        "time": 1
      },
      "bgName": "bg_story_task"
    },
    {
      "actor": 10700050,
      "side": 2,
      "dir": 1,
      "nameColor": "#a9f548",
      "hidePaintEquip": true,
      "say": "For example, if your final goal is to become a top idol, your short-term goals would be to make each and every performance memorable.",
      "typewriter": {
        "speed": 0.05,
        "speedUp": 0.01
      },
      "painting": {
        "alpha": 0.3,
        "time": 1
      },
      "bgName": "bg_story_task"
    },
    {
      "actor": 10700050,
      "side": 2,
      "dir": 1,
      "nameColor": "#a9f548",
      "expression": 4,
      "hidePaintEquip": true,
      "say": "That also gives us an idea of how we want to structure our lessons for each performance, so we always have something to work towards.",
      "typewriter": {
        "speed": 0.05,
        "speedUp": 0.01
      },
      "painting": {
        "alpha": 0.3,
        "time": 1
      },
      "bgName": "bg_story_task"
    },
    {
      "actor": 10700050,
      "side": 2,
      "dir": 1,
      "nameColor": "#a9f548",
      "expression": 2,
      "hidePaintEquip": true,
      "say": "Why don't you try setting some short-term goals and start from there?",
      "typewriter": {
        "speed": 0.05,
        "speedUp": 0.01
      },
      "painting": {
        "alpha": 0.3,
        "time": 1
      },
      "bgName": "bg_story_task"
    },
    {
      "actor": 10700030,
      "side": 2,
      "dir": 1,
      "nameColor": "#a9f548",
      "hidePaintEquip": true,
      "say": "(As expected from Ritsuko. Her advice is always so insightful!)",
      "typewriter": {
        "speed": 0.05,
        "speedUp": 0.01
      },
      "painting": {
        "alpha": 0.3,
        "time": 1
      },
      "bgName": "bg_story_task"
    },
    {
      "say": "That seems manageable enough.",
      "actor": 401230,
      "side": 2,
      "dir": 1,
      "nameColor": "#a9f548",
      "typewriter": {
        "speed": 0.05,
        "speedUp": 0.01
      },
      "painting": {
        "alpha": 0.3,
        "time": 1
      },
      "bgName": "bg_story_task"
    },
    {
      "say": "If we treat the performance and the lessons as a package... Then, how about we schedule a concert two months out? I'll plan out the lessons with that timetable in mind.",
      "actor": 401230,
      "side": 2,
      "dir": 1,
      "nameColor": "#a9f548",
      "typewriter": {
        "speed": 0.05,
        "speedUp": 0.01
      },
      "painting": {
        "alpha": 0.3,
        "time": 1
      },
      "bgName": "bg_story_task"
    },
    {
      "actor": 201010,
      "side": 2,
      "dir": 1,
      "nameColor": "#a9f548",
      "say": "...Huh?!",
      "typewriter": {
        "speed": 0.05,
        "speedUp": 0.01
      },
      "action": [
        {
          "y": 45,
          "type": "shake",
          "dur": 0.15,
          "number": 2,
          "delay": 0,
          "x": 0
        }
      ],
      "painting": {
        "alpha": 0.3,
        "time": 1
      },
      "bgName": "bg_story_task"
    },
    {
      "say": "(She skipped straight to the scheduling?!)",
      "actor": 201010,
      "side": 2,
      "dir": 1,
      "nameColor": "#a9f548",
      "typewriter": {
        "speed": 0.05,
        "speedUp": 0.01
      },
      "painting": {
        "alpha": 0.3,
        "time": 1
      },
      "bgName": "bg_story_task"
    },
    {
      "actor": 10700050,
      "side": 2,
      "dir": 1,
      "nameColor": "#a9f548",
      "hidePaintEquip": true,
      "say": "In that case... Let's start by making sure everyone has the songs memorized and the choreography ready to go.",
      "typewriter": {
        "speed": 0.05,
        "speedUp": 0.01
      },
      "painting": {
        "alpha": 0.3,
        "time": 1
      },
      "bgName": "bg_story_task"
    },
    {
      "actor": 10700030,
      "side": 2,
      "dir": 1,
      "nameColor": "#a9f548",
      "expression": 3,
      "hidePaintEquip": true,
      "say": "Huh? W-wait, Ritsuko?",
      "typewriter": {
        "speed": 0.05,
        "speedUp": 0.01
      },
      "painting": {
        "alpha": 0.3,
        "time": 1
      },
      "bgName": "bg_story_task"
    },
    {
      "actor": 10700030,
      "side": 2,
      "dir": 1,
      "nameColor": "#a9f548",
      "expression": 3,
      "hidePaintEquip": true,
      "say": "(Wait, why are you acting like you're a part of this?!)",
      "typewriter": {
        "speed": 0.05,
        "speedUp": 0.01
      },
      "painting": {
        "alpha": 0.3,
        "time": 1
      },
      "bgName": "bg_story_task"
    },
    {
      "say": "I see now. After that, we'll be able to adjust the choreography and figure out how to improve on the singing.",
      "actor": 401230,
      "side": 2,
      "dir": 1,
      "nameColor": "#a9f548",
      "typewriter": {
        "speed": 0.05,
        "speedUp": 0.01
      },
      "painting": {
        "alpha": 0.3,
        "time": 1
      },
      "bgName": "bg_story_task"
    },
    {
      "say": "Then, we'll need to have group lessons that focus on piecing together everyone's individual parts, in addition to the solo lessons.",
      "actor": 401230,
      "side": 2,
      "dir": 1,
      "nameColor": "#a9f548",
      "typewriter": {
        "speed": 0.05,
        "speedUp": 0.01
      },
      "painting": {
        "alpha": 0.3,
        "time": 1
      },
      "bgName": "bg_story_task"
    },
    {
      "actor": 10700050,
      "side": 2,
      "dir": 1,
      "nameColor": "#a9f548",
      "hidePaintEquip": true,
      "say": "That's precisely right!",
      "typewriter": {
        "speed": 0.05,
        "speedUp": 0.01
      },
      "action": [
        {
          "y": 45,
          "type": "shake",
          "dur": 0.15,
          "number": 2,
          "delay": 0,
          "x": 0
        }
      ],
      "painting": {
        "alpha": 0.3,
        "time": 1
      },
      "bgName": "bg_story_task"
    },
    {
      "actor": 10700030,
      "side": 2,
      "dir": 1,
      "nameColor": "#a9f548",
      "expression": 3,
      "hidePaintEquip": true,
      "say": "(At this rate...)",
      "typewriter": {
        "speed": 0.05,
        "speedUp": 0.01
      },
      "painting": {
        "alpha": 0.3,
        "time": 1
      },
      "bgName": "bg_story_task"
    },
    {
      "actor": 201010,
      "side": 2,
      "dir": 1,
      "nameColor": "#a9f548",
      "say": "(This conversation is going bottoms up...!!)",
      "typewriter": {
        "speed": 0.05,
        "speedUp": 0.01
      },
      "action": [
        {
          "y": 45,
          "type": "shake",
          "dur": 0.15,
          "number": 2,
          "delay": 0,
          "x": 0
        }
      ],
      "painting": {
        "alpha": 0.3,
        "time": 1
      },
      "bgName": "bg_story_task"
    },
    {
      "actor": 10700050,
      "side": 2,
      "dir": 1,
      "nameColor": "#a9f548",
      "hidePaintEquip": true,
      "say": "Also, when we get to that point, there's another thing we need to be careful about when it comes to lessons...",
      "typewriter": {
        "speed": 0.05,
        "speedUp": 0.01
      },
      "painting": {
        "alpha": 0.3,
        "time": 1
      },
      "bgName": "bg_story_task"
    },
    {
      "actor": 10700030,
      "side": 0,
      "dir": 1,
      "nameColor": "#a9f548",
      "action": [
        {
          "y": 45,
          "type": "shake",
          "dur": 0.15,
          "number": 2,
          "delay": 0,
          "x": 0
        }
      ],
      "expression": 3,
      "hidePaintEquip": true,
      "say": "Alright, t-time out, you two!!",
      "subActors": [
        {
